#: App.LocalizationContent.dataSource.dataSourceType.jira.templates.projects.desc
msgid "This function retrieves all projects visible to the currently logged-in user. If user credentials are not provided, it only returns public projects. For more information, refer to the following keys: issueTypes, lead, and projectKeys."
